info.author: John Wiseman
info.description:
lemonodor app framework.

INSTALL
=======

::

    $ pip install lemapp

USAGE
=====

...

DEVELOP
=======

::

    $ git clone http://github.com/wiseman/lemapp lemapp
    $ cd lemapp
    $ make

RUNNING TESTS
=============

::
    $ make test
